snippet.title: Monster Meals - Trailer
snippet.description:
Monster Meals is a cooking game where you control a small monster chef in your food truck, preparing meals with exotic creatures for monstrous customers. Serve quickly before you become the next meal!

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3021850/Monster_Meals/
